{"tid":330882,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點算？打開房門唔小心發現到我細佬睇緊.......","createTime":"2017-07-21T15:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T23:59:37.000Z","uid":62294,"like":423,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"cd22b2fa374bfe2037ed2d0866257eba184d3d4b","tid":330882,"uid":62294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:46:50.000Z","msg":"今日我做完嘢早咗返屋企、打開房門，<br />\n見到我細佬睇緊Youtube 笑到卡卡聲，<br />\n我諗住行近啲睇吓佢睇緊咩啦......<br />\n聽到把聲有啲熟口面、一睇！<br />\n<br />\n屌！係笑波子！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為話說我之前有同我細佬一齊恥笑過笑波子嗰啲低能Youtuber... 所以佢見到我喺後面就即刻Close咗個分頁... 極老尷<br />\n我咩都冇講就出返房.....<br />\n<br />\n我成晚都仲未同佢講過嘢.... 我想叫佢唔好再睇但又驚佢唔鍾意<br />\n請問我應該講咩同點先勸到佢唔好再睇呢啲片....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位Ching有冇咩好方法？"},{"pid":"562698a046819c3518faaecef4c233e05c26f7a8","tid":330882,"uid":21423,"like":11,"dislike":156,"score":-145,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2cf90173ef456196597fba1cee52e271b296c88","tid":330882,"uid":34977,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾返你兩粒波子佢笑下囉</blockquote><br />\n哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43caf39c71a5e958be3551a4c6c54d048b9ddf42","tid":330882,"uid":77948,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"屌 以為係AV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb04021a87687a3b134849b9a58dfa9a996c5cb","tid":330882,"uid":62294,"like":281,"dislike":1,"score":280,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 以為係AV <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n衰過AV呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm